# AquaSense - HackOrbit Aqua Sync ğŸš€ğŸ’§

AquaSense is an end-to-end water quality monitoring and analysis system built for HackOrbit 2025. It combines IoT-based data collection, a backend API, and a machine learning model for predictive analysis, with a clean React-based frontend dashboard.

